  "detailed_description": "<strong>Alone and underground. Transport items to repair the ruins of a vanished civilization. Maybe you will find your way back to the surface. Go challenge yourself in this game called \"Onder\".</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>key features :</strong></h2><br><strong>Explore the remaining ruins of an established civilization underground safe from all human forms</strong><br>----------------------------------------<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393360/extras/10e519d8e3778ebfe94b0487ae20e842.avif?t=1733943305\" width=250 height=80 /></span><br>----------------------------------------<br><strong>Solve puzzles left behind during the apocalypse</strong><br>----------------------------------------<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393360/extras/eb0cd472d2b3226e82064d50576e0ae9.avif?t=1733943305\" width=250 height=80 /></span><br>----------------------------------------<br><strong>Carrying items can help you along your underground journey</strong><br>----------------------------------------<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393360/extras/f62dc152301bcdb08f4477457593c8c0.avif?t=1733943305\" width=250 height=80 /></span><br>----------------------------------------<br><strong>Creative Mode, Build what you want and share your maps with friends</strong><br>----------------------------------------<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393360/extras/4af7b8b2d3d517e2963bfdc9c782d39c.avif?t=1733943305\" width=250 height=80 /></span><br>----------------------------------------",
